-for-kids-video-call-1-83-camera-oem-factory-gps-smartwatch-for-children\">YQT T53</a> Рђћ рЃЋрЃўрЃЊрЃћрЃЮ рЃќрЃљрЃарЃў, рЃЊрЃўрЃЊрЃў рЃћрЃЎрЃарЃљрЃюрЃў</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/products/video-call-hot-selling-cheap-kids-smart-watch-4g-network-lbs-wifi-location-voice-call-small-size-for-kids\">YQT T46</a> Рђћ рЃЋрЃўрЃЊрЃћрЃЮ рЃќрЃљрЃарЃў, рЃЎрЃЮрЃЏрЃърЃљрЃЦрЃбрЃБрЃарЃў</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>рЃўрЃ«рЃўрЃџрЃћрЃЌ <a href=\"/products\">рЃАрЃарЃБрЃџрЃў рЃЎрЃљрЃбрЃљрЃџрЃЮрЃњрЃў</a> рЃЊрЃљ рЃљрЃўрЃарЃЕрЃўрЃћрЃЌ рЃЉрЃљрЃЋрЃерЃЋрЃўрЃАрЃЌрЃЋрЃўрЃА рЃерЃћрЃАрЃљрЃцрЃћрЃарЃўрЃАрЃў рЃЏрЃЮрЃЊрЃћрЃџрЃў.</p>','<h2>What Is School Mode?</h2>\r\n<p>School mode is a feature that <strong>blocks the watch screen during lesson hours</strong>. The child cannot see notifications, open the menu, or play games Рђћ the watch only shows the time. This keeps teachers happy and the child focused on learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Enable School Mode</h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Open the <strong>Setracker2</strong> app</li>\r\n<li>Go to <strong>Settings Рєњ Do Not Disturb</strong></li>\r\n<li>Add a time interval (e.g., 09:00-14:00)</li>\r\n<li>Select weekdays (Monday-Friday)</li>\r\n<li>Save Рђћ the mode activates automatically</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2>What Stays Available in School Mode?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>SOS button</strong> Рђћ emergency call always works</li>\r\n<li><strong>Parent call</strong> Рђћ parents can call the child</li>\r\n<li><strong>GPS tracking</strong> Рђћ location monitoring continues in the background</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>All other functions Рђћ camera, games, voice messages Рђћ are blocked.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Geo-fence Рђћ School Perimeter</h2>\r\n<p>In Setracker2, parents set a <strong>safe zone around the school</strong> (radius 100-1000 meters). If the child leaves the zone, the parent receives an <strong>instant notification</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>This is especially useful when the school is near a busy road or the child walks to school alone.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>GPS History Рђћ Where Was the